2004-08-19  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* modules/userspec: Don't depend on alloca.

2004-08-17  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* MODULES.html.sh: Add xalloc-die, c-strtod, c-strtold, raise,
