	* gnulib-tool (func_all_modules): Ignore files ending in ~.
	* MODULES.html.sh: Likewise.

2003-01-09    <karl@gnu.org>

	* MODULES.html.sh: include `dirname $0` in PATH, to find
	gnulib-tool.

